your crummy movie anyway.

199
00:10:14,614 --> 00:10:16,914
Yeah.
We'll take our business elsewhere.

200
00:10:16,991 --> 00:10:18,281
You know, Bart.

201
00:10:18,367 --> 00:10:22,077
