with his bare hands.

379
00:19:30,836 --> 00:19:33,626
That's "B-A-R-E" hands.

380
00:19:33,714 --> 00:19:36,264
Although modern historians
recently uncovered evidence

381
00:19:36,341 --> 00:19:38,761
